originalText.text: Dr. Adebayo is by far the best doctor I've visited. He is very thorough, honest and respectful. His office is very clean and the staffs are amazing. From my personal experience the wait time to be seen is anywhere from 5 to 10 minutes. I recommend that you book your appointments with Dr. Adebayo.

originalText.text:
Went in for a routine physical and got everything but that. The wait was long and the receptionists and nurses were rude. Dr. Adebayo himself is OK, but I only got to see him after a special request and after being talked to by another very unprofessional physician, Dr. Taylor.
On top of the bad experience, the office overcharged me (despite the fact that my visit was fully covered by insurance) and I'm now STILL waiting for a reimbursement check that should have arrived in November. Seriously, don't go here. It's not worth it.
